5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1003030, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "O Allah bless Muhammad and his family O Allah I bear witness that this is Your Revealed Book from You, To Your messenger Muhammad son of Abdullah, Allah’s blessings be on him and his family. And it is Your Spoken Words, through the tongue of Your Prophet, You have made it a guide from You to Your creation, And a connecting rope between You and Your servants. O Allah I have opened Your Covenant and Your Book.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Ay Ma’bood! Mai gawahi deta hu keh yeh Teri kitaab (Qur’an) hai jo Teri jaanib se naazil huwi hai Tere aakhri Rasool Muhammad (s.a.w.a) ibne Abdullah par aur yeh Tera kalaam hai jo Tere Nabi (s.a.w.a) ki zabaan se zaahir huwa hai jise Tu ne apni taraf se apni makhlooq ka haadi banaya hai aur yeh woh rassi hai jo Tere bando’n ke darmiyaan tani huwi hai. Ay Ma’bood! Be-shak mai ne Tere hukm naame aur Teri kitaab ko khola hai.", "Urdu": "اے معبود! میں گواہی دیتا ہوں کہ یہ تیری کتاب (قرآن)ہے جو تیری جانب سے نازل ہوئی ہے تیرے آخری رسول محمدؐ ابن عبداﷲؐ پر اور یہ تیرا کلام ہے جو تیرے نبی ؐ کی زبان سے ظاہر ہوا ہے جسے تونے اپنی طرف سے اپنی مخلوق کا ہادی بنایا ہے اور یہ وہ رسّی ہے جو تیرے بندوں کے درمیان تنی ہوئی ہے اے معبود! بے شک میں نے تیرے حکم نامے اور تیری کتاب کو کھولا ہے۔", "RArabic": "INSHA-ALLAH COMING SOON", "ArabicText1": "اَللّٰهُمَّ اِنِّيْ اَشْهَدُ اَنَّ هٰذَا كِتَابُكَ الْمُنْزَلُ مِنْ عِنْدِكَ عَلٰى رَسُوْلِكَ مُحَمَّدِ بْنِ عَبْدِ اللهِ صَلَّى اللهُ عَلَيْهِ وَآلِهٖ وَكَلَامُكَ النَّاطِقُ عَلٰى لِسَانِ نَبِيِّكَ جَعَلْتَهٗ هَادِيًا مِنْكَ اِلٰى خَلْقِكَ وَحَبْلًا مُتَّصِلًا فِيْمَا بَيْنَكَ وَبَيْنَ عِبَادِكَ۔ اَللّٰهُمَّ اِنِّيْ نَشَرْتُ عَهْدَكَ وَكِتَابَكَ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1010079, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "O Allah, so make my looking at it an act of worship and my reciting it a pondering, and my pondering over it, a way to derive lessons. (O Allah) include me from those who are advised by the narrations of its advices, and who avoid Your disobedience. (O Allah) do not seal my ears when I’m reciting it and do not place a curtain over my sight, Nor make my recitation a recitation lacking pondering, Rather make me from among those who ponder over its verses and its rules, Deriving the ways to Your religion, and do not make me heedless when I’m looking at it, nor make my reciting a waste. Surely You are the Most Gentle, the Most Merciful.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Ay Ma’bood! Pas is par mere nazr karne ko ibaadat aur meri tilaawat ko is par gaur aur mere is gaur ko nasihat qaraar de aur mujhe un logo’n mein rakh jo is mein Tere bayaan se nasihat haasil karte hai aur Teri na-farmaaniyo’n se dar-kinaar (dur) rehte hai aur iski tilaawat ke waqt mere kaan bandh na kar, meri aankho’n par pardah na daal aur meri tilaawat ko aisi tilaawat na bana jis mein gaur o fikr na ho bal keh mujhe aisa bana de keh mai iski aayato’n aur ehkaam par gaur karu aur Tere deen ke usool maaloom karu aur us par meri nazr ko be-tawajjohi aur meri tilaawat ko be-faaida na bana, be-shak Tu bohot maher-baan bade rahem waala hai.", "Urdu": "اے معبود! پس اس پر میرے نظر کرنے کو عبادت اور میری تلاوت کو اس پر غور اور میرے اس غور کو نصیحت قرار دے اور مجھے ان لوگوں میں رکھ جو اس میں تیرے بیان سے نصیحت حاصل کرتے ہیں اور تیری نافرمانیوں سے دور رہتے ہیں اور اس کی تلاوت کے وقت میرے کان بند نہ کر میری آنکھوں پر پردہ نہ ڈال اور میری تلاوت کو ایسی تلاوت نہ بنا جس میں غور وفکر نہ ہو بلکہ مجھے ایسا بنادے کہ میں اس کی آیتوں اور احکام پر غور کروں اور تیرے دین کے اصول معلوم کروں اور اس پر میری نظر کو بے توجہی اورمیری تلاوت کو بے فائدہ نہ بنا بے شک تو بہت مہربان، بڑا رحم والا ہے۔", "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": "اَللّٰهُمَّ فَاجْعَلْ نَظَرِيْ فِيْهِ عِبَادَةً وَقِرَاءَتِيْ فِيْهِ فِكْرًا وَ فِكْرِيْ فِيْهِ اعْتِبَارًا وَاجْعَلْنِيْ مِمَّنِ اتَّعَظَ بِبَيَانِ مَوَاعِظِكَ فِيْهِ وَاجْتَنَبَ مَعَاصِيَكَ وَلَا تَطْبَعْ عِنْدَ قِرَاءَتِيْ عَلٰى سَمْعِيْ وَلَا تَجْعَلْ عَلٰى بَصَرِيْ غِشَاوَةً وَلَا تَجْعَلْ قِرَاءَتِيْ قِرَاءَةً لَا تَدَبُّرَ فِيْهَا بَلِ اجْعَلْنِيْ اَتَدَبَّرُ آيَاتِهٖ وَ اَحْكَامَهٗ، آخِذًا بِشَرَائِعِ دِيْنِكَ وَلَا تَجْعَلْ نَظَرِيْ فِيْهِ غَفْلَةً وَلَا قِرَاءَتِيْ هَذَرًا اِنَّكَ اَنْتَ الرَّءُوْفُ الرَّحِيْمُ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedS